{"tid":34502,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"港航機飛北海道引擎故障 緊急折返降落","createTime":"2016-12-11T13:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T07:53:55.000Z","uid":1194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e17a9366d9aa3e86d6e340555482d4456e8fc97e","tid":34502,"uid":1194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:31:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161211&amp;guid=56033561&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161211%26guid%3D56033561%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=q7VntjqcN0D1Vxs6osFulHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=70527413\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161211%26guid%3D56033561%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=1bc068c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161211&amp;guid=56033561&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港航一班編號HX690的客機，原定今早9時15分出發前往日本北海道，惟起飛後不久，懷疑引擎故障，機長決定折返香港機場。<br />\n<br />\n港航回應事件時稱，香港航空上午9時34分由香港往札幌的HX690航班，在起飛後，由於其中一個引擎出現問題，按既定程序折返。航機於上午9時58分安全降落香港機場，已經即時調配受影響航班上的270名乘客轉乘另一航機，並於下午3時的前往目的地。<br />\n<br />\n機管局表示，早上9時50分接獲機場控制塔通知，指一部港航客機須緊急降落，該客機於9分鐘後安全著陸。<br />\n<br />\n根據flightradar24網站的資料，涉事的HX690航機型號是空中巴士A330-343，於早上9時34分起飛，大約9分鐘後攀升至4,800呎左右時，飛至擔杆島的上空突然折返，然後在9時58分抵達香港國際機場。"},{"pid":"58b28146d0977d4462224f664cd8621b5f631d7c","tid":34502,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:18:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾海南航空<br />\n掛住香港個名　但支那級數既水準 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd641035dc9b3e829e0abf9db4d8f077f698407","tid":34502,"uid":38351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾海南航空<br />\n掛住香港個名　但支那級數既水準 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪就係<br />\n成日做promote 堅係平，話時話我有啲厭世，係咪應該買重保險後瘋狂搭？"},{"pid":"adf599957a148a98e11c7b8ae9ddaf643eab9fca","tid":34502,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>垃圾海南航空<br />\n掛住香港個名　但支那級數既水準 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪就係<br />\n成日做promote 堅係平，話時話我有啲厭世，係咪應該買重保險後瘋狂搭？</blockquote><br />\n雖然我對呢間航空公司無乜好感<br />\n但你九成九九九都係撘都到破產都未claim到保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5976ab11a30c23231569bdde579b45a62914b8e","tid":34502,"uid":1194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>垃圾海南航空<br />\n掛住香港個名　但支那級數既水準 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪就係<br />\n成日做promote 堅係平，話時話我有啲厭世，係咪應該買重保險後瘋狂搭？</blockquote><br />\n雖然我對呢間航空公司無乜好感<br />\n但你九成九九九都係撘都到破產都未claim到保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquo