m到保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同保險公司對賭不如同何生賭"},{"pid":"6d0c58f43086f7638ca09a79b607ab82349b25a6","tid":34502,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>垃圾海南航空<br />\n掛住香港個名　但支那級數既水準 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪就係<br />\n成日做promote 堅係平，話時話我有啲厭世，係咪應該買重保險後瘋狂搭？</blockquote><br />\n雖然我對呢間航空公司無乜好感<br />\n但你九成九九九都係撘都到破產都未claim到保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n保險公司同支那人一樣咁無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔關事<br />\n係講緊你搭到破產架機都好難會炒<br />\n引擎故障都要睇程度,佢而加個case頂盡咪單邊故障<br />\n對機師黎講簡直小菜一碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩個都收晒皮既可能性係極低<br />\n你想撞正架機出事+救唔返 機會率唔會高過你中六合彩幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d86384f46c4486e4cd2d384587bf52fa34a157f","tid":34502,"uid":43470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那以本傷人<br />\n<br />\n所以我一直支持國泰<br />\n海南未坐過<br />\n海南廉航都係坐過1次 (個fd指定要坐)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國泰咪又係國航做大股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1001fddcae0f07dc392ded9e83bd9d2ffcdb9f","tid":34502,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支那以本傷人<br />\n<br />\n所以我一直支持國泰<br />\n海南未坐過<br />\n海南廉航都係坐過1次 (個fd指定要坐)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國泰咪又係國航做大股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n太古45%<br />\n國航29.99%係互渣春袋 為打入中國航線無計...至少&quot;暫時&quot;唔係100%紅底"},